O Lord, You have been good,
You have been faithful 
To all generations;

O Lord, Your steadfast love
And tender mercy
Have been our salvation.

O Lord, You have been good,
You have been faithful 
To all generations;

O Lord, Your steadfast love
And tender mercy
Have been our salvation.

For by Your hand
We have been fed
And by Your Spirit
We have been led.

O Lord, You have been good,
You have been faithful
To all generations.

For by Your hand
We have been fed
And by Your Spirit
We have been led.

O Lord, Almighty God,
Father unchanging,
Upright and holy.

O Lord, You have been good,
You have been faithful
You have been good.

You have been good,
You have been faithful
You have been good.

